---
title: Quick Japanese-Style Chicken Schnitzel with Katsu Sauce & Radish Slaw
description: Give chicken schnitzel a Japanese-inspired twist by serving it with a killer katsu sauce and crisp radish slaw. It's a crowd-pleasing combo that's surprisingly carb smart. Prepare for repeat requests!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
